title: Coinbase adds support for USDC on Stellar
description:
Coinbase has added support for USD Coin (USDC) on Stellar, the Stellar Development Foundation (SDF) said on June 23. That announcement indicates that Coinbase will allow both withdrawals and deposits of Circle’s stablecoin via the Stellar network. title: Tanzanian Central Bank Says Quoting Prices in Foreign Currency Against the Law
description: The Bank of Tanzania (BOT) has reiterated that shillings remain the East African country’s sole legal tender. The apex bank said residents quoting prices in foreign currency or those refusing payment in Tanzanian shillings are in violation of the Bank of Tanzania Act 2006.
